FAQ

What can I download?

Instagram Reels/Posts/IGTV (public) and YouTube videos including Shorts/Live/Long.

How does preview & download work?

Click Preview to load the media. Then click Download (the green button below the preview) to save it to your device.

Is it free?

Yes. InstantSaver is free and does not require any signup.

Why canâ€™t I download private Instagram content?

Private posts and stories require login and user permission. InstantSaver supports public posts only.
